		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_TAR_DINUUEN_SPIDER_THROWER_STRATEGY">
			<Text>The Spider Thrower is Tar-Dinuu's unique unit, replacing the Archer. Spider Throwers are available after researching Pottery instead of Archery. After attacking an enemy, it has a chance to inflict Spider Bite on them, which has a chance of causing them to lose 15 HP each turn while in their enemy's territory and 5 HP while in neutral territory.</Text>
